  <h1>A2 — Broken Authentication</h1>
  <p class="muted">Problems in authentication or session management that allow attackers to impersonate users.</p>
  <h3>Teaching note</h3>
  <p>Avoid storing plaintext passwords and do not rely on predictable sessions.</p>
  <h3>Mitigations</h3>
  <ul><li>Hash passwords with a strong algorithm (bcrypt/argon2).</li><li>Enforce multi-factor where relevant and secure session cookies (HttpOnly, Secure).</li></ul>
  <h3>Where to patch</h3>
  <p>Check login code in <code>app/routes.py</code> and password storage in your DB schema.</p>
